          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 4402,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Should specific, minor gaps in the existing framework be identified following a proper enforcement review, the correct and proportional legislative approach would be targeted,",
        "chunk_meta": {
